screen_name: @holly_bourneYA Thank you everyone! This has been super helpful, knowing we’re not alone. My COVID 19 test came out positive. I had fever, chills, headaches and body aches for three days and on day four I completely lost my sense of taste and smell.  It’s been four weeks and I have recovered 60%
